data.description: Discover your perfect retreat in this charming 1-bed, 1-bath gem nestled on 3.73 acres. Ideal for AirBnb or a cozy hunting cabin, this tiny home promises serenity and adventure. Located in vibrant Downtown Ellijay, relish in delightful eateries and boutique shops. Embrace nature with apple picking and scenic hikes just moments away. Your tranquil escape awaits! Four-wheel-drive will be needed          NOTE: Principals of the seller may share ownership in a licensed real estate brokerage.            Buyer offered $1000 credit at closing with the use of the seller's preferred lender!
